title: Loveless (001 - 024) (2005 - 2008) (digital) (Son of Ultron-Empi
description:
Set after the Civil War the title follows Wes Cutter and his wife Ruth as they go back to their hometown of Blackwater to exact revenge on those that have wrong them.

Wes and Ruth Cutter are running from the horror of the Civil War and its savage aftermath. Now wanted, they're drawn to life as outlaws as they travel through the untamed West. By the white-hot team of Brian Azzarello & Marcelo Frusin
